    "description_long": "This is a modern, rectangular wooden TV cabinet with a light natural wood finish and minimalist design. The cabinet features three drawers on the left, a large sliding door in the center with a muted blue-gray color, and a smaller sliding door on the right in a darker gray. On top of the cabinet sits a flat-screen television, a small potted plant, and a remote control, all arranged neatly. The cabinet stands on four slender, black metal legs, giving it a slightly elevated appearance. The overall look is clean and contemporary, suitable for urban living spaces or communal areas.",
